      "effect": "2+ \"D/D\" monsters\nYou can target 1 \"D/D\" or \"Dark Contract\" card you control; destroy it, also, during your Main Phase this turn, you can conduct 1 Pendulum Summon of a \"D/D\" monster(s) in addition to your Pendulum Summon. (You can only gain this effect once per turn.) When your opponent activates a monster effect in the hand (Quick Effect): You can banish 1 \"D/D\" monster and 1 \"Dark Contract\" card from your GY; negate the activation. You can only use this effect of \"D/D/D Sky King Zeus Ragnarok\" once per turn.",
